title: Trap Shooting Automation with AI
description: This course was specially designed to instruct learners on how to leverage artificial intelligence concepts, tools and programs to automate trap shooting.
learningObjectives: Understand the theory of trap shooting
Design AI programs for trap shooting.
Develop and execute trap shooting automation.

finalProjectDetails.overview: Design, develop and execute a fully-functional AI program for trap shooting automation.
finalProjectDetails.submissionInstructions: Submit your AI design documentation, code files, recorded demo and written report through the course learning portal.
